## Verification Plan
### Automated
- `npm run lint` (frontend) passes.
- `npm run test` (unit) all green.
- Cypress suite runs without failures.

### Manual
- Serve app with `npm run start` and open in Chrome; verify layout on mobile viewport.
- Build Android APK with `npm run build && npx cap add android && npx cap copy && npx cap open android` and inspect UI.
- Test login, order creation, real‑time tracking, feedback submission.
- Verify admin routes are inaccessible without admin JWT.

